divs: Sighting Detailsit's second day I go outside my house at 5am to see if I see more of these lights, and seen strange since more than 5 and all with different speed and direction, the most rare is to see some so close together, they make me once deduce that there are planes, also for their speed ... these days'll continue going until you are sure that they are those lights across the sky, a light flickered a stronger and brighter than a plane .. . continue in my research.
